#PersonalFinance

*PersonalFinance* is a web application for personal financial management, developed with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to record financial transactions, organize them by category, view reports, and access them via authentication.

---

## Features

- ✅ Income and expense tracking
- ✅ Custom category management
- ✅ Reports by category (totals)
- ✅ User authentication
- ✅ Responsive interface
- ✅ Local backend with JSON server
- ✅ Frontend development with Vite

---

## Technologies used

- HTML5 + CSS3 (with responsive design and CSS variables)
- Modern JavaScript (ES Modules)
- Vite as a frontend development server
- JSON server as a mock backend

---